I could pull it off.

536
00:45:42,625 --> 00:45:44,505
But seeing it all come together…

537
00:45:44,585 --> 00:45:45,705
Makes you proud, huh?

538
00:45:47,745 --> 00:45:48,585
Yes.

539
00:45:49,625 --> 00:45:51,225
You should be proud.

540
00:45:51,305 --> 00:45:54,465
Because honestly,
you're far more capable than you think.

541
00:46:01,785 --> 00:46:05,345
By the way, Mudmee,
are you doing better now?

542
00:46:07,545 --> 00:46:10,745
Well, I'm doing better.

543
00:46:10,825 --> 00:46:12,705
But where I am in life,

544
00:46:12,785 --> 00:46:14,825
there's always something
to deal with every day.

545
00:46:17,785 --> 00:46:19,745
Then next time you're not feeling okay,

546
00:46:19,825 --> 00:46:22,345
why don't you try visiting
an art exhibition?

547
00:46:22,425 --> 00:46:25,865
It helps you relax and enjoy yourself too.

548
00:46:25,945 --> 00:46:26,945
I do it all the time.

549
00:46:27,025 --> 00:46:30,145
I think it's better
than going out drinking.

550
00:46:35,145 --> 00:46:38,145
In that case, would you take me?

551
00:46:42,905 --> 00:46:46,345
Well, if I'm not busy, sure.

552
00:46:51,345 --> 00:46:52,865
-Come on, let's go inside.
-Okay.

553
00:46:52,945 --> 00:46:55,305
This is our signature drink.
Make sure to get some shots.

554
00:46:55,385 --> 00:46:56,745
Sure.

555
00:46:57,785 --> 00:47:00,265
Will this drink make me float?

556
00:47:00,345 --> 00:47:01,665
Right up on a cloud.

557
00:47:01,745 --> 00:47:02,905
Totally.

558
00:47:02,985 --> 00:47:06,305
And this area is our workshop section…

559
00:47:42,225 --> 00:47:43,705
Dr. Namking.

560
00:47:43,785 --> 00:47:45,505
Congratulations, Piang.

561
00:47:50,745 --> 00:47:52,665
The bouquet is a bit large.

562
00:47:52,745 --> 00:47:57,305
I wanted to congratulate you,
and use it as an apology too.

563
00:47:57,385 --> 00:47:59,665
I'm sorry I missed
our first date that day.

564
00:49:20,425 --> 00:49:22,105
Congratulations, Piang.

565
00:49:40,825 --> 00:49:42,505
Are you okay?

566
00:49:43,905 --> 00:49:45,785
I've been feeling a little drained today.

567
00:49:52,265 --> 00:49:54,825
Then, why don't you get some rest?

568
00:50:03,825 --> 00:50:05,385
If you're tired,

569
00:50:05,465 --> 00:50:07,785
we don't have to do anything tonight.

570
00:50:08,305 --> 00:50:10,425
Just relax.

571
00:50:10,505 --> 00:50:12,105
Or go to sleep if you want.

572
00:50:12,625 --> 00:50:14,505
I'll stay right here with you.

573
00:50:20,745 --> 00:50:22,025
<i>Song.</i>

574
00:50:22,545 --> 00:50:23,625
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

575
00:50:23,705 --> 00:50:24,985
<i>I really can't go on anymore.</i>

576
00:50:25,065 --> 00:50:26,545
<i>No, Neung. Don't do this.</i>

577
00:50:26,625 --> 00:50:28,225
<i>And don't forget to keep your promise.</i>

578
00:50:28,305 --> 00:50:29,865
No!

579
00:50:41,905 --> 00:50:43,065
Did you have a nightmare?

580
00:50:48,385 --> 00:50:49,465
I'm sorry.

581
00:50:58,265 --> 00:50:59,745
It's okay.

582
00:51:04,065 --> 00:51:05,305
Go back to sleep.

583
00:51:06,345 --> 00:51:07,425
Come on.

584
00:51:21,185 --> 00:51:23,185
Bad dreams, be gone.

585
00:51:24,665 --> 00:51:25,945
What are you doing?

586
00:51:27,865 --> 00:51:29,425
Calling your spirit back.

587
00:51:29,505 --> 00:51:32,825
When I had nightmares as a kid,
Mudmee always did this.

588
00:51:33,505 --> 00:51:36,065
Then I'd sleep through the night
without bad dreams.

589
00:51:40,225 --> 00:51:41,985
You don't have to be scared.

590
00:51:42,505 --> 00:51:44,065
It was just a dream.

591
00:51:44,145 --> 00:51:45,545
It's not real.

592
00:51:47,705 --> 00:51:49,785
What if it really happened before?

593
00:51:50,385 --> 00:51:54,985
Well, just think of it as
something that's already passed.

594
00:51:55,785 --> 00:51:57,705
And don't let it hurt you again.

595
00:52:02,705 --> 00:52:04,425
Song, don't be afraid.

596
00:52:06,545 --> 00:52:08,825
I'll be your dreamcatcher.

597
00:52:15,985 --> 00:52:17,785
Then stop pushing me away.

598
00:53:05,825 --> 00:53:08,185
<i>Didn't we agree not to do this?</i>

599
00:53:08,265 --> 00:53:10,745
<i>I was just making desserts for the café</i>

600
00:53:10,825 --> 00:53:12,505
<i>and wanted you to try them.</i>

601
00:53:12,585 --> 00:53:13,825
How about we date?

602
00:53:13,905 --> 00:53:18,065
Usually, you don't talk
to many people, do you?

603
00:53:18,705 --> 00:53:21,345
Maybe when I warned you
to stay away from Piang,

604
00:53:21,425 --> 00:53:22,345
it wasn't enough.

605
00:53:22,425 --> 00:53:23,585
<i>At Dr. Namking's birthday party,</i>

606
00:53:23,665 --> 00:53:25,105
<i>I'm sure you saw</i>

607
00:53:25,185 --> 00:53:28,505
<i>that where you stand</i>
<i>and where Piang stands are worlds apart.</i>

608
00:53:32,545 --> 00:53:34,545
<i>I'll disappear from Piang's life.</i>

